{"tid":2376926,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"曾鈺成暗批梁振英無完整解讀《基本法》 《大公報》護梁斥曾鈺成「斷章取義」","createTime":"2021-01-23T07:18:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-23T11:31:09.000Z","uid":240362,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"68a72df9a2c9a79729ed7bcfe62a3d4c14314346","tid":2376926,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T07:18:50.000Z","msg":"建制陣營再就下任特首產生辦法各執一詞。繼早前全國政協副主席梁振英主張以協商產生特首，隨即被特首林鄭月娥反駁指「以選舉產生比較好」後。前立法會主席曾鈺成借受訪暗批梁振英未有完整解讀《基本法》，認為用協商「是退步而不是進步」，有違「循序漸進」，不過《大公報》評論文章又間接反駁曾鈺成「斷章取義」，其說法令人「莫名其妙」。<br />\n<br />\n《基本法》第45條列明，特首在當地通過選舉或協商產生，由中央任命。特首產生辦法按香港實際情況和循序漸進原則而規定，最終達至由廣泛代表性的提名委員會按民主程序提名後普選產生。同時，45條亦列明具體的特首產生辦法由《基本法》附件一規定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210123/2AVH3SA5FBARHFIPVZED64AQEY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210123%2F2AVH3SA5FBARHFIPVZED64AQEY%2F&d=0UfJYUPH4CcS6uVeskuI5J4W3gw9R4Gr2eBBN4Jm0fY%3D&h=8941571c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210123%2F2AVH3SA5FBARHFIPVZED64AQEY%2F&h=f9314bc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210123/2AVH3SA5FBARHFIPVZED64AQEY/</a>"},{"pid":"055412ad77e59b7fce01b9f4e0d909e85518958e","tid":2376926,"uid":65651,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T07:21:56.000Z","msg":"又用呢招 共狗最叻拉一派打一派<br />\n借d意扮內閧拎民心<br />\n咁我知下年特首支那想邊個做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c0e6c35287c618541f5753cee3f79ad81b5cde2","tid":2376926,"uid":18477,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T07:28:39.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">是撚但啦兩面都係垃圾</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8rxiyfJ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8rxiyfJ.gif&h=eaec7133&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d238cc058f5a6958ac862033d7dbdca41b643623","tid":2376926,"uid":27122,"like":0,